    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I believe this race is resolved by the second part of [the check in `accept_new_socket`](https://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/master/src/core/lib/iomgr/tcp_uv.cc#L246) that checks for the presence of `uv_socket->accept_socket`. That `accept_socket` field is set in [`uv_socket_accept`](https://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/master/src/core/lib/iomgr/tcp_uv.cc#L287), the same function that sets the `accept_cb` field. So, it won't try to call that callback unless it has been set."
  },
